{"word":"ἀνιμάω","slug":"ἀνιμάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνιμάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to draw up</i> water, by means of leather straps: generally, <i>to draw out</i> or <i>up</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: also <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <el>ἀνιμῶμαι</el>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> (<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>ἑαυτόν</el>), <i>to mount up</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}